  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Kudu Batti' Mattoo with powder at Rajagiri",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Organized criminal Nadun Chinthaka Wickramaratne alias Harak Kata, a strong member of the drug network Kudu Rajina alias (Kudu Batti) and another person were arrested on Rajagiriya Kotte road with heroin drugs worth over 15 lakh rupees, the Special Task Force said.",
        "Police seized 51 grams, 600 milligrams of heroin and two mobile phones in the possession of the suspect.",
        "The raid was carried out based on a tip-off received by the officers of the 2nd Organized Crime Unit of the Police Special Task Force.",
        "The arrested suspect is 34 years old and the suspect is 40 years old."
      ],
